channel.description:
Welcome to my new server currently in the making.
First off: Levels: So far ive gotten: farming working 100% Runecrafting 100% Thieving (Got picklocking done) Fletching Almost complete Smithing 75% woodcutting (gives cash)
[b]Commands:[/b]
xslime Bowtomaster New clanwarsNew 50% jadNew gaiNew Just seen and thought be funny :) logs2planksNew 20% skateboard New Loads of pet commands New chill New Membership New fart New actual stat Eat Armorhelp Pest New Rep Pure Slave New Skiller New Notedbarrows Pnpc Xteletome Xteleto God Godoff Sweet New items Home New Mypk Suggest Master Silab Clicks Macrowarn Getpass Setlvls New Male New Female New Empty Mystats Theifmenu Castlewars New Rich New items added Mypos Bank Tele Checkip Hitdiff (not quite sure what this does) Drainme New 99hp New
[url=http://img27.imageshack.us/my.php?image=godwars.jpg][img=http://img27.imageshack.us/img27/9271/godwars.th.jpg][/url] [url=http://img27.imageshack.us/my.php?image=fartskill.jpg][img=http://img27.imageshack.us/img27/2074/fartskill.th.jpg][/url] [url=http://img27.imageshack.us/my.php?image=clanwarsv.jpg][img=http://img27.imageshack.us/img27/2551/clanwarsv.th.jpg][/url] [url=http://img27.imageshack.us/my.php?image=dbmini.jpg][img=http://img27.imageshack.us/img27/4651/dbmini.th.jpg][/url] [url=http://img27.imageshack.us/my.php?image=logs2planks.jpg][img=http://img27.imageshack.us/img27/8436/logs2planks.th.jpg][/url] [url=http://img27.imageshack.us/my.php?image=saraside.jpg][img=http://img27.imageshack.us/img27/7753/saraside.th.jpg][/url]
More but thats enough to say for the moment.
[b]Control panel Put On.[/b]
[b]Starting Armour[/b]
Rune helm Rune plate Dragon legs Climbing boots Rune defender whip obby cape wooden shield (for the lols) str ammy
[b]starter place[/b]
Updates: Bankpin 50% barrage 90% fart skill 100% gladiators (can be an audience or fight)
Changed to varrock Bank
Some npcs added And some shops.
[b]Custom places[/b]
Added elve mages shops
Added elve mages fighting area
Added mining area
Added the little building from monkey madness where u have to answer questons at the gate
[b]Custom Places added[/b]
A new pk box Batonae (Random name Lol quite cool though)
Games: Godwars Cwars Clanwars pointspk (Rewards)
Custom minigames: Dark bow minigame 100% Jurrasic park 100%
EDIT: I Now have working Normal magic teleports wich i figured out for myself Lol , and also working emote teles Thanks for a suggestion from Killer-bros-owner Suggesting me to start maybe completing the towns Like lumb camelot with like npcs objects Things like that Thanks for your time ---------------------------------------------------
Sorry i couldnt get pics, might be able to soon.
Rate me :D For a beginner coder im not relly experienced :D :) :) :D
